{"tid":1053484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"童顏巨乳女兵愛玩槍　身材超暴力！網友暴動：想當欄杆","createTime":"2019-03-09T06:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T05:48:23.000Z","uid":147522,"like":28,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5810967b2b6f1cbc311931941f503733eb59b55c","tid":1053484,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:09:57.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯爆乳妹，又正身材又暴力，PTT表特板鄉民激推爆！<br />\n<br />\n一名網友在PTT表特板分享「俄羅斯小龍女！」美照，照片中的俄羅斯正妹皮膚白皙、長相可愛，還有著一副超暴力的豐滿身材，有時又是甜美鄰家少女，有時又穿上軍裝，提槍化身成性感女大兵，穿著緊身背心的她姣好身材嶄露無遺，還有幾張美臀陷在欄杆裡的照片更是令人想入非非，讓許多網友紛紛讚嘆「住手 欄杆是無辜的 衝著我來」「我投降 隨意妳處置吧」「超級無敵夭壽讚」「好暴力的身材」「想當欄杆」「這個奶、這個尻、這個腹肌」「幹，戀愛了！」<br />\n<br />\n據了解，這名俄羅斯辣妹叫做伊蓮娜(Elena Deligioz)，因為超高顏值加上姣好身材，卻是個超級軍事迷引發反差，在網路上有不小名氣，因為爸爸就是一名軍官，所以從小就是軍事迷，喜歡玩一些軍事模型、槍械等，IG上自稱是「俄羅斯小龍女」，目前有超過12萬粉絲追蹤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wiTDAST.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwiTDAST.png&h=9cc092fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3rmNucU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3rmNucU.png&h=7fb74576&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VyS1yEA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVyS1yEA.png&h=13e47cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qoa22xW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQoa22xW.png&h=00cb82eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b0b7ccfdff212a93a610b99fd9c3bf9888d2e84","tid":1053484,"uid":37384,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:11:39.000Z","msg":"幾時過黎玩我支鎗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3790b0711f07142b164df5dd24eca40b8cce109","tid":1053484,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img